| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2327 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 18132829-87ea-59bc-96e9-b26c11a3a83f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
